it's certainly the first step.

54
00:02:10,350 --> 00:02:13,500
I always struggled in school
and felt like a failure.

55
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:16,020
Interestingly, when I
left and started working

56
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:18,660
