165
00:06:42,787 --> 00:06:45,630
"Steal Like An Artist" echoes this point

166
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:48,600
when it suggests to copy
from multiple inspirations

167
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:51,510
until you have a mix
that is truly original.

168
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:54,210
Having this unique skill stack
will give you the ability

169
00:06:54,210 --> 00:06:55,590
