182
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:29,340
but lots of people don't
see the value of investing.

183
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:30,360
Let me ask you this.

184
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:33,000
Would you rather have $3 million now

185
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:36,810
