turns into 10.7 million.

188
00:07:42,607 --> 00:07:45,600
"The Compound Effect" uses
this analogy to demonstrate

189
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:48,660
the power of investing and
gaining compound interest.

190
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:50,400
Once most people get
their head around this,

191
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:53,700
