255
00:10:23,070 --> 00:10:26,100
each worth between 3 and $2,000.

256
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,540
That's an amazing deal.

257
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:29,850
These three stocks can
help you start building

258
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:32,250
your investment portfolio right away.

259
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:36,450
Level two, 100,000 to $1 million.

260
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:39,090
Now that you fixed all
your internal beliefs

