329
00:13:37,890 --> 00:13:40,770
Furthermore, these businesses
went on to dominate

330
00:13:40,770 --> 00:13:43,890
their industries for 10
to 15 years after launch.

331
00:13:43,890 --> 00:13:46,530
A good strategy for
creating your own blue ocean

332
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:48,690
